00:42:00,648 --> 00:42:11,760
It is to make the tea with absolute attentiveness and compassion, and then to accidentally spill it all over.

360
00:42:11,780 --> 00:42:24,413
After you've done that a few times, you'll stop asking.

361
00:42:25,135 --> 00:42:35,083
Yes, there's nothing more off-putting than somebody asking you to be compassionate out of moral duty.

362
00:42:36,666 --> 00:42:40,510
It undermines the whole idea of being compassionate.

363
00:42:40,530 --> 00:42:41,269
So, I don't know.

