00:42:50,458 --> 00:42:51,239
Is it patient acceptance by any chance?

368
00:42:51,340 --> 00:42:51,739
It is, yes.

369
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:53,742
Patient acceptance, yes.

370
00:42:54,717 --> 00:42:55,978
Patient acceptance.

