00:48:46,594 --> 00:49:14,829
and you may find that even in your meditation great feelings of sorrow about one's past actions comes and it's feeling that sorrow which is the process of cleansing the heart as you work on that path of forgiveness then of course you have to come down to the very base of why it is that you're behaving like that and then you come across the self

